GCBoard NEWS -- history of user-visible changes. 30 May 2004

Version 0.3.0
* Converted to Gtk2.0.  The GtkCBoard widget now also supports
  pixbufs als image type.  This allows for nice effects such
  as transparent pieces.

Version 0.1.0

* Initial release.  This release contains the Gtk1.2 version, and Ruby
  language bindings.  Most of the features are implemented, except for
  resizing, premove and transformation (and any to come :-).
  Documentation is not written yet.
